<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3385708>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Macrobrachium chainatense sp. nov. (male). (A) Entire animal, lateral view; (B) telson and uropod; (C) carapace, top view; (D) scaphocerite; (E) epistome; (F) mandible; (G) maxillula; (H) maxilla; (I) first maxilliped; (J) second maxilliped; (K) third maxilliped; (L) first pereiopod; (M) second pereiopod; (N) third pereiopod; (O) uropodal diaeresis spine. Scales: (A) 5 mm; (B–N) 1 mm, (O) 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3385708/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

